Text: Yeah I guess it’s because the body’s confused since it’s such a rapid switch? Idk but I’m hoping with practice it will all sort out eventually. Here’s to hoping I guess

Author: fragilemndstrongmind
Text: Honestly it's harder for me to just eat regular meals and workout "reasonable" times than to run/bike hours or wait until dinner. Today I had breakfast and lunch and I just couldn't focus, it almost felt like a headache.
